{"tid":2310423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英外交部料 20萬港人移民　BNO申請人數急增　料今年底達 73 萬人","createTime":"2020-12-03T08:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T19:20:45.000Z","uid":30561,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da7b545cee963c162523a99cf0fe0a31bca8d1d7","tid":2310423,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/外媒-英外交部料-20-萬港人移民-bno-申請人數-6-月起急增-料今年底達-73-萬人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92-%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E6%96%99-20-%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-bno-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8-6-%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E-%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E9%81%94-73-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=86360acd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92-%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E6%96%99-20-%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-bno-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8-6-%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E-%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E9%81%94-73-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=28913c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/外媒-英外交部料-20-萬港人移民-bno-申請人數-6-月起急增-料今年底達-73-萬人/</a><br />\n<br />\n「英國國民海外護照」（BNO）持有人明年起可申請最多 5 年期簽證，之後申請定居英國。英國媒體 The Telagraph 引述當地外交部外洩的內部文件（leaked internal briefing paper ），自今年 6 月 BNO 申領人數急增，預料 BNO 持有人數目將在今年底突破 73 萬，較今年 2 月激增約 110%。報道又指，英國外交部預計將會有 20 萬名持 BNO 或合資格人士，由香港移民到英國。<br />\n<br />\n據報道引述的內部內文，截至今年 8 月，BNO 持有人數目已增至超過 40 萬，目前仍有多於 20 萬的申請尚待處理。而自今年 7 月起，當局發出的 BNO 數目大增，按英國內政部預計，BNO 持有人的數目有可能在今年年底增至 733,000 人。<br />\n<br />\n另據法新社早前引述英國官方數字報道，自去年 6 月反修例運動開始後，BNO 持有人數目急劇增加，在 8 至 12 月便有 9 萬多人獲發 BNO，較 2018 年整年獲發數目多 8 倍；截至今年 10 月，今年再有近 17 萬人獲發 BNO，在港 BNO 持有人數目累積至近 47 萬人。"},{"pid":"53255492ca673f34d45abebc50241aa46e5a5af1","tid":2310423,"uid":33618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"我哋一齊返祖國啦"},{"pid":"087526ee0c5cdd7f5c79b42ec9b3ed8931ab02dd","tid":2310423,"uid":366470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53255492ca673f34d45abebc50241aa46e5a5af1","tid":2310423,"uid":33618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"我哋一齊返祖國啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"返屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4cc7dfc526e9ce431ca6de0f46e4383f6d2413","tid":2310423,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔計已經有外國護照(超過百萬)<br />\n再加BNO或其他移民，即係有成200萬人離開"},{"pid":"3d52f5477b38bc6bac378280dd3052e295b82cab","tid":2310423,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4f4cc7dfc526e9ce431ca6de0f46e4383f6d2413","tid":2310423,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔計已經有外國護照(超過百萬)<br />\n再加BNO或其他移民，即係有成200萬人離開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"睇樓價就知唔會啦，咪戇鳩啦"},{"pid":"382046a8a3c804c948d79e434b3a479b8d608c1f","tid":2310423,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d52f5477b38bc6bac378280dd3052e295b82cab","tid":2310423,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4f4cc7dfc526e9ce431ca6de0f46e4383f6d2413","tid":2310423,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔計已經有外國護照(超過百萬)<br />\n再加BNO或其他移民，即係有成200萬人離開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"睇樓價就知唔會啦，咪戇鳩啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"二手跌緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9310d089b0e09a915ff3e63ff6c81fdc6558eaa8","tid":2310423,"uid":4826,"like":0,"di